	<h1 class="title">让难民们也活得有尊严，宜家设计了一个避难所</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-02 13:07:36 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18391/medium/18391.jpg?1449031084" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18391" data-title="《让难民们也活得有尊严，宜家设计了一个避难所》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18391/medium/18391.jpg?1449031084" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18391.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
